Web Server: Raspberry pi 3
-----------------------------
1. Install Express JS
2. replace app.js in local system with the app.js available here
3. include test.js available here into routes folder in express JS
4. include all the web pages and images and dependencies into public folder in express JS
5. install noble npm package for running discovery from web server
6. Download web_server.js to local system 

BLE nodes: Raspberry pi 3
-----------------------------
1. install bleno and noble npm package for discovery and advertisement
2. Download ble_node.js into these ble nodes

Initialization:
-----------------------------
1. Run express JS in web server
2. Run command '$sudo node ble_node.js' in ble nodes in the mesh network 
